//===- MultiFloatTrigTables.h - vendored trig tables ----------------------===//
//
// Per-N Taylor coefficient tables for sin and cos polynomials in z=rx²,
// plus 1/π constant. Generated by tools/gen_trig_tables.jl. Do not edit.
//
// Algorithm: scale input by 1/π, take |·|, reduce by π/2 quartiles
// (n = round(2*|x/π|)), residual rx ∈ [-1/4, 1/4]. Evaluate:
//   sin(π*rx) = rx * Σ kSinCoefs[k] * z^k    (z = rx²)
//   cos(π*rx) = Σ kCosCoefs[k] * z^k
// then select sin / cos / -sin / -cos based on the quadrant (n mod 4).
//===----------------------------------------------------------------------===//

